ed spin axis orientation and equatorial velocity\nof the planet can be estimated. We conclude that the RMse effect could be a\npowerful method to measure exoplanet spins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2015 10:28:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-06"}
